{"tid":281070,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]用完hdmi 3in1之後個mon no signal","createTime":"2017-06-12T12:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T13:14:35.000Z","uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a01e37fda6b39c0e5df5d661a89cfff9acf561a4","tid":281070,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:32:27.000Z","msg":"未用之前淨係一條hdmi由pc插落Mon<br />\n跟住因為想插埋ps4，買咗個hdmi 3in1switch<br />\n一插完ps4有畫面冇聲，pc直頭冇畫面<br />\n拆返出黎淨係插pc都係冇畫面<br />\n淨插ps4又係有聲冇畫面<br />\nkeyboard,mouse全部有電，cpu同display風扇有轉<br />\n都唔知係邊樣出問題<br />\ngoogle咗勁耐<br />\n個Mon reset settings又試過<br />\npc抆電源鳩等30分鐘又試過<br />\npc拎走cmos電池又試過<br />\n都係no signal<br />\n唔係個爛鳩switch可以整壞個Mon/pc咁on9呀？"},{"pid":"f8e523650dc462f5bb6b8d34f54f144de4d07621","tid":281070,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2a59355fd48c4b3d160d7f9c7f91139b60c7a8","tid":281070,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4888a031dd3d0ceca4dbcc4d7edd11a96798242b","tid":281070,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee7da76c8cd3dd65f9d32bb9087aefec2837565","tid":281070,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd9626266dfae961340d1283bc1a91512e22c6b","tid":281070,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:05:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9d1a5d7629fad4441ed43fc73755ffc352b117","tid":281070,"uid":51408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply